<a class="jsShowSpoiler spoilerAction">(view spoiler)</a><span class="spoilerContainer" style="display: none">[Near the end Silas visits the mayor and Voncille after his attack, expecting to be reprimanded. Instead he is informed that he is being promoted. I don't understand the following exchange: <br />[Silas:] "I can't take none of it. Not yet. You got to wait till the paper comes out."<br />"Why?" the mayor asked. "What's in the paper?"<br />"You just got to wait"... Is it revealed later what appears in the paper, or did I miss it? <a class="jsHideSpoiler spoilerAction">(hide spoiler)</a>]</span>
